casebody.data:
No. 65,

Misc.

Roark v. Alvis, Warden. Petitioner pro se. William Saxbe, Attorney General of Ohio, and William M. Vance, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari denied.
